These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, swimming, cycling
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##8
3. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |    3     |
| Sport   | cycling | swimming | cricket |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, writing, gardening
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is not to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##8
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3     |
| Hobby   | collecting | gardening | writing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, mirinda, lemonade
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |  3  |
| Beverage   | mirinda | iced-tea | lemonade |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, sprite, fanta
1. the person drinking sprite is not to the left of the person drinking fanta##8
2. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |  2   |      3      |
| Beverage   | fanta | sprite | coffee |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-5::.
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, thai, nigerian
1. the thai is in an even position##4
2. the thai is not to the right of the nigerian##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3     |
| Nationality   | egyptian | thai | nigerian |

